    name: "voidapply.com",
    description: "Apply for jobs faster than everyone else, straight to the void!",
    htmlDescription: `<h1>VoidApply</h1>
<p><strong>Apply faster than ever. Right to the void.</strong></p>
<p>A satirical job board with parody ATS interfaces that lets you fill out an application and rejects you immediately. Built as catharsis for everyone who&#39;s applied to 200 jobs and heard back from 0.</p>
<hr>
<h2>What it does</h2>
<ol>
<li>Search for a job</li>
<li>Fill out a full application</li>
<li>Get rejected, instantly</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2>Tech</h2>
<ul>
<li>Vite + React 18 + TypeScript</li>
<li>React Router v6 — URL is the source of truth</li>
<li>Tailwind CSS v3 + Framer Motion</li>
<li>Fuse.js for client-side fuzzy search</li>
<li>No backend. No APIs. Pure static SPA.</li>
<li>Deployed with Cloudflare Pages</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2>ATS Skins</h2>
<p>Parody clones of real applicant tracking systems:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>WorkNight</strong> — Workday. Eight steps to submit a CV you already uploaded.</li>
<li><strong>GreenHouse of Pain</strong> — Greenhouse. AI screening badge, passion scale, instant regret.</li>
<li><strong>Talaeo</strong> — Taleo/Oracle. Early-2010s enterprise UI. Session timeout. Misaligned fields.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Rejection Modes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Dev Null</strong> — <code>cat application.pdf | /dev/null</code></li>
<li><strong>Ghost</strong> — Spinner, then silence. Forever.</li>
<li><strong>Speedrun</strong> — REJECTED in 0.003 seconds. World record: Amazon, 0.002s.</li>
<li><strong>Fake Email</strong> — A personalized rejection from HR. Your CV will be kept on file. 4...3...2...1. Deleted.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2>Development | Quick Start Guide</h2>
<pre><code class="language-bash">npm install
npm run dev
</code></pre>
<pre><code class="language-bash">npm run build   # production build
npm run test    # vitest
</code></pre>
<h2>Debugging</h2>
<p>You should be able to find everything you need for debugging the ATS skins and Rejection modes at <code>/debug</code></p>
`,
